  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<b>家中有打印机就可制作。纸条隐蔽性强，传播灵活安全。可结合 厕所革命和图书馆革命 一起使用。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>注意不要留下指纹！</b><br/>\n<br/>\r\n正面<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9sbVVoc2pmLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/lmUhsjf.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lmUhsjf.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lmUhsjf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n带剪裁虚线 背面<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Dc2FzNEd4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Csas4Gx.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Csas4Gx.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Csas4Gx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n不带剪裁虚线 背面（需将A4复印纸竖着对折一次，横着对折两次产生折痕，方便剪裁。优点是，剪裁出来的纸条不会出现虚线印记）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9LRWpJenlBLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/KEjIzyA.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KEjIzyA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KEjIzyA.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n三张图片 网盘下载：https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1KfZHibXEPyka--qqEJdu1g17NZ3fGas-?usp=sharing<br/>\n<br/>\r\n使用场景：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n1、坐公交车，放在座位上面；<br/>\r\n2、用透明胶粘在厕所门上；<br/>\r\n3、夹在图书馆的书里面；<br/>\r\n4、放在同学书包或行人购物袋里面<br/>\r\n5、\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
